<a id="phase-1"></a>
## Phase 1: Project Structure Analysis

### Technology Stack (Verified)

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|---|---|---|
| Frontend framework | Next.js | 16.1.4 |
| UI library | React | 19.2.3 |
| Styling | TailwindCSS | 4.1.18 |
| State/Data | React Query | 5.62 |
| Backend | Express.js | 4.18.2 |
| ORM | Prisma Client | 5.10.0 |
| Database | MySQL | — |
| Cache/Queue | ioredis | 5.9.2 |
| AI | Ollama (local) | 0.6.3 |
| Social | Baileys (WhatsApp), Telegram Bot API, Facebook Graph API | — |
| Validation | Zod | 3.22.4 |

### Architecture Pattern

**Monorepo** with two distinct packages:

```
news-platform-next/
├── src/               ← Next.js 16 Frontend (Atomic Design)
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── (public)/  ← 12 public pages (home, article, category, login, etc.)
│   │   └── admin/     ← 10 admin modules
│   ├── components/    ← atoms → molecules → organisms → templates
│   ├── services/      ← 13 frontend API services
│   ├── contexts/      ← AuthContext
│   └── types/         ← TypeScript type definitions
│
└── server/            ← Express.js Backend
    ├── src/
    │   ├── routes/     ← 11 route files ("fat controllers")
    │   ├── services/   ← 17 service files
    │   ├── middleware/ ← auth, cache, errorHandler, rateLimiter
    │   ├── validators/ ← Zod schemas
    │   └── config/     ← env validation
    └── prisma/         ← schema + migrations + seed
```

