<a id="phase-3"></a>
## Phase 3: Business Logic Review

### 3.1 Critical Logic Issues

| # | Issue | File | Severity |
|---|---|---|---|
| B1 | **Slug collision race condition** — checks `findUnique` then creates, but concurrent requests can collide | [article.routes.ts:261–267](file:///c:/Users/MahmoodCenter/Desktop/news-platform-next/server/src/routes/article.routes.ts) | High |
| B2 | **No transaction for article creation** — article, tags, activity log created in separate queries | article.routes.ts | High |
| B3 | **Cascade delete on User model** deletes ALL articles when user is deleted | [schema.prisma:93](file:///c:/Users/MahmoodCenter/Desktop/news-platform-next/server/prisma/schema.prisma) | **Critical** |
| B4 | **No soft-delete** for any entity — hard deletes permanently destroy data | All delete endpoints | High |
| B5 | **RSS article cleanup deletes pending articles** after 30 days — editor may not have reviewed them yet | [rss.service.ts `cleanupOldArticles`](file:///c:/Users/MahmoodCenter/Desktop/news-platform-next/server/src/services/rss.service.ts) | Medium |
| B6 | **Social posting marked as "auto-completed"** in scheduler without actually posting | [scheduler.ts:82–88](file:///c:/Users/MahmoodCenter/Desktop/news-platform-next/server/src/services/scheduler.ts) | High |
| B7 | **Automation pipeline has no idempotency guard** — retry can create duplicate articles | [automation.service.ts `publishToPlatform`](file:///c:/Users/MahmoodCenter/Desktop/news-platform-next/server/src/services/automation.service.ts) | High |
| B8 | **AI rewrite failure silently skips** — no admin notification or retry mechanism beyond manual action | automation.service.ts | Medium |

### 3.2 Edge Cases Not Handled

- RSS feed returns items with missing `pubDate` — could crash date parsing
- Image download fails during article creation — `finalImageUrl` may be undefined
- Duplicate feed URL check uses client-side array, not unique constraint enforcement
- Comment nested replies have `onDelete: SetNull` — orphaned reply chains

