<a id="phase-9"></a>
## Phase 9: Admin Workflow Simulation

### 9.1 Workflow: Adding a New RSS Source

| Step | Action | Issues Found |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Click "مصدر جديد" | ✅ Clear CTA |
| 2 | Fill source name, URL, logo | ✅ Form is intuitive |
| 3 | Add RSS feed URLs with categories | ⚠️ No URL validation preview — can't test if URL returns valid RSS before saving |
| 4 | Save | ⚠️ No feedback on whether feed URL is valid |
| 5 | Fetch articles | ✅ Works, shows count |

> **Missing:** RSS URL validation/preview before committing

### 9.2 Workflow: Article Publishing Pipeline

| Step | Action | Issues Found |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | RSS feed auto-fetches articles | ✅ Every 15 min |
| 2 | Admin reviews in moderation queue | ⚠️ No bulk preview — must open each article individually |
| 3 | Approve article | ⚠️ Triggers automation pipeline — no "approve without automating" option |
| 4 | AI rewrites article | ❌ If Ollama is down, article gets stuck in `AI_PROCESSING` forever |
| 5 | Article published to platform | ⚠️ No preview before publication |
| 6 | Social media posting | ❌ Posts marked "auto-completed" without actually verifying delivery |

### 9.3 Workflow: Editing Existing Article

| Step | Action | Issues Found |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Navigate to articles list | ✅ Paginated list |
| 2 | Click edit | ✅ Article form loads |
| 3 | Modify content | ⚠️ No autosave, no unsaved changes warning |
| 4 | Save | ⚠️ No visual diff of changes |
| 5 | Changing status to PUBLISHED | ❌ Re-triggers social posting with no duplicate check |

### 9.4 Workflow: Deleting Content

| Step | Action | Issues Found |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Delete RSS source | ❌ Cascades delete ALL feeds + ALL articles — no impact preview |
| 2 | Delete article | ❌ Hard delete — no recovery possible |
| 3 | Delete user | ❌ Cascades delete ALL user's articles — catastrophic data loss |

